import React from 'react'
import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, Tab, Tabs } from '@mui/material/'

export const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <AppBar>
                <Toolbar>
                    <Typography>CineNumen</Typography>
                            <Tabs>
                                <Tab label='Cartelera' />
                            </Tabs>
                </Toolbar>
            </AppBar>
        </>
    )
}
